title: Simply Pimpin- Give Me Your Number
description:
Simply Pimpin is an Arizona Hip Hop & Rap group comprised of 4 individuals, all of different backgrounds with one thing on their mind. MONEY and SUCCESS in life. With money comes freedom and with freedom comes choices. This groups diversity of skill levels in life, combined with melodic flows of pain, struggle, and everyday life, has successfully launched them to the top of their game locally. They want to be heard internationally.
This is one of their best top hits! "Give Me your Number"
Go check Simply Pimpin out at
